About this item

  • EASY SLIP ON STYLE: It is a convenient slip-on design slipper, along with a comfortable made super soft plush fleece lining that encompasses your feet very well and offers soothing comfort. Made of 100% Polyester Microfiber plush lining offers superior comfortability.
  • ANTI-SLIP & FLEXIBLE DURABLE RUBBER SOLE: Non-slip and flexible rubber sole to protect every step of the way, perfect for indoor and outdoor family use. cooking in the kitchen, playing with your kids, drinking afternoon tea in the courtyard. watering the lawn, walking the dog, or signing for parcels
  • CUSHIONED FOOTBED: Reclaim comfort even on the busiest of days in these comfy leopard slippers. These slides with fluffy lining pamper your feet in all-day coziness at home or office. Featuring pillow-soft memory foam insole for lasting cushioning support, this casual slipper will also be a perfect update to your bedroom footwear collection
  • PERFECT GIFT CHOICE: A pair of warm and cozy home slippers, great gifts for girlfriend wife mom daughter sister, and your loved ones to express your Christmas & New Year warmest greetings. It will be a great surprise for your lovers and family. We offer a range of sizes, including S/M fits 6 to 8, M/L fits 8 to10
  • WASH & CARE: Machine wash cold gentle cycle, do not bleach, lay flat to dry, do not iron, do not dry clean

      Product Description

      Ergonomic comfort meets luxury. Keep your feet warm with sophistication as you wear these MIRMARU All Over Plush Slippers. These memory foam cushioned slip-ons relieve the pressure from your feet while providing your soles the therapeutic support they need. The overall plush offers a warm and soothing sensation so you'll feel like walking in the clouds. Made from the finest quality materials and construction, each pair is assured to be durable and resilient to wear and tear so it's a perfect long-term companion. They provide warmth during chilly seasons and enough insulation on warmer days, making it an all-weather pair of slippers. Available in a variety of bright and cool colors, these scuffs will definitely become your instant favorite!

      How customer reviews and ratings work

      Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

      To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
